text: Rockville is the county seat of Montgomery County, Maryland, United States. According to the 2020 census, the city had a total population of 67,117, making it the fourth largest incorporated city in Maryland. == References == Category:Cities in Montgomery County, Maryland Category:County seats in Maryland Category:1717 establishments Category:1710s establishments in the Thirteen Colonies Category:18th-century establishments in Maryland
